            "title": "盤中速報 - 旭然(4556)股價拉至漲停，漲停價80.6元，成交233張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭然(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4556:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4556\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4556-TW</a>)02日13:02上漲7.3元，股價漲停報80.6元，委買5,000張、委賣6,000張，成交233張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為過濾分離設備及周邊產品之研發、設計、製造與銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>旭然(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4556:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4556\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4556-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.66%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.46%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-18 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-19 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>融資增減：-65 張</li> <li>融券增減：-10 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
